{"tid":1373694,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"打破困局 唔該法律巴打入嚟 想問下民事告班黑警有無得諗","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:04:40.000Z","uid":220864,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ee38784cfa9bf2c21335c9637d6d546488cc86c4","tid":1373694,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:05:03.000Z","msg":"其實<br />\n好撚肯定而家你點同個政權講黑警濫權<br />\n佢都係話：咁你去投訴囉<br />\n就係有呢塊免死黑牌<br />\nd黑警先可以肆無忌憚<br />\n<br />\n為左打破呢個困局<br />\n我有幾個問題想請教下連登法律巴絲<br />\n<br />\n1. 如果我有證據 例如 片，相，證明有黑警利用過份武力，例如鄭柏林拗手腕個單野，如果我清楚影到佢個警員編號，可唔可以遁民事告佢？ 法庭會唔會受理？<br />\n<br />\n2. 係咪一定要愛害者先可以告？<br />\n<br />\n3. 律師費大概幾多，或者total費用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 天文數字嘅話我諗難d阻嚇到班狗<br />\n<br />\n4. 如果上面問題係我on9,我見民事法入面有行政法，照copy就係<span style=\"color: teal;\">制定行政法是為了保障個人權益，以防政府或公共機構濫用權力。</span>，代表意思係咩"},{"pid":"dfa5b01c4265105d9745d3b304dae3f44c06a4c2","tid":1373694,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:05:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9dccdd4cde9ac31841d2f60780595f58b455de73","tid":1373694,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6712e66deb5d37e3b51697ced3a5712fcd16db43","tid":1373694,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:06:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39c0bfc5cf595b8a76ac96d34063f49522a537f5","tid":1373694,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b12d935a534696082751a8043f3241aa8853d9c","tid":1373694,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae03ee84a99dd24990a61dadade287af2d21886c","tid":1373694,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:07:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91131766cb25635c597f33a045192f7bab7c6e0e","tid":1373694,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"